Package poker.model.logic.showdown Description

This package contains all classes that are needed for the showdown. It contains a class to determine the winner of a specific pot, which uses another class which evaluates the hand for a player.

Additionally it contains a class to evaluate card combinations and their winning chances.
Author:
Becker
